     v4 — 2026-04-16: Added tape_cost_per_m + bubble_cost_est
     ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     Tape baseline: OPP 48mm × 100m roll @ ฿30 → ฿0.30/m
     Tape formula (auto-computed by model):
       tape_length_m = [(W + H) × 2 × 3 rounds + 20 cm] ÷ 100
       tape_cost_est = tape_length_m × tape_cost_per_m

     Bubble wrap estimate: Based on typical product fragility
     and interior surface coverage per box size category.
     Baseline: แผ่นบับเบิ้ล 50m × 100cm roll @ ฿350 = ฿0.07/cm²
